{"id":318856,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/维权网-成都访民维权「简报」第四十期/","date":"2013-10-19T21:02:48Z","modified":"2013-10-19T21:02:48Z","title":"维权网 | 成都访民维权「简报」第四十期","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span> </span></p>\n<div><span> </span><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span>                                      </span></span></span><span>（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2013.10.1-10.15</span></span><span>）</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span>  </span></span></span><span>宗旨：给政府提供维稳线索；留下访民辛酸足迹（冰山一角）</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>1</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>1</span></span><span>日，成都市锦江区龙舟路办事处访民姜雪梅，从今天深夜开始每晚受到骚扰，已经持续一周。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>1</span></span><span>日，成都市锦江区强拆访民彭天惠、严塔凤，新都叶尚洪，青白江区林德群，进京上访，他们先到美领事馆递交材料，没被受理，后他们到人权。强拆访民彭天惠、严塔凤被截访人员拦截送回。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>3</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2</span></span><span>日，成都青羊文家董家村二组何艾芩，发现有人到她家骚扰，她打</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>110</span></span><span>报警，警察来后既不佩戴警号，也不履行职责，相反还说：你们上访人员我们不管，就是打死也不关我们的事。于是她到派出所求助，派出所仍此态度，于是她打迪到省委冲进大门求助，后被警察强制带到黄花街派出所。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>4</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>7</span></span><span>日，成都高新区学生＂右派＂罗开文，到青羊区法院交诉讼成都市公安局行政诉讼的立案材料。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>5</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>7</span></span><span>日，成都市青羊区人民北路街道办强拆访民陈茜丈夫林龙华，因在家对冲进她家对他行凶的不明人员采取正当防卫而被行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>天，今天出狱。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>6</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>8</span></span><span>月，成都青羊区光华办事处董春模、青羊区东坡办事处杨邦会到省委上访。因她们房屋被强拆多年没解决，于是她们今天直接冲进省政府大门高喊，要求省长魏宏出来接受她们的投诉。后被警察控制抬出送到信访办。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>7</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>8</span></span><span>号，都江堰崇义镇江安村</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>组</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>5.12</span></span><span>学生遇难母亲周兴容，到省委上访，省委接待人员让她到成都市市委上访。等她到市委上访，接待人员再次推诿她到都江堰市委反映。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>8</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>8</span></span><span>日，成都青羊区草市街办事处强拆访民廖才俐，到办事处找到政法委领导陶雪璐要求解决问题。接待人员表示，他们只能组织协调解决。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>9</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>8</span></span><span>日，成都高新区学生＂右派＂罗开文，到省公安厅询问他今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>3</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>19</span></span><span>上交的复议材料的答复。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>000197</span></span><span>警员答复，现在仍在调查复核中。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>8</span></span><span>号，成都锦江区访民黄远清、唐德英、郭玉彬到省人大上访。人大接待人员给她们到省政府信访办的上访归口单。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>11</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>8</span></span><span>日，成都市锦江区访民彭天惠、李仁玉到成都市中院，讯问她们到遂宁旁听案件审理而被控的上诉立案情况。接待法官说还没收到。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>12</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>8</span></span><span>日，成都市锦江区访民李仁玉到省高院讯问她前夫被冤入狱申诉的立案情况。接待人员说该案已结。李说她没接到接案通知书。在她坚持下，接待法官才答应再查查。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>13</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>8</span></span><span>日，成都市锦江区龙舟路办事处访民姜雪梅，接到自称是锦江区政府工作人员的电话，问她是否在家，目的是要监控确认她的行踪。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>14</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>8</span></span><span>日，成都市锦江区狮子山街道办事处六四遇难母亲唐德英，到省纪委、省检察院、成都市检察院交“对合法公民冤死在看守所的投诉书”的上访材料。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span>  </span></span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>15</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>日，成都锦江区访民唐德英、郭玉彬到市纪委上访。一个张姓接待人员接待了她们。接待人员表示，她会把她们反映的问题尽快反馈到市政府去，希望他们尽快解决。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>16</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>日，成都市锦江辜素芳出院。由于她家房屋被强拆多年没解决，上访多次被打压，加上儿子因拆迁被失踪至今无下落，她身体被拖垮，多种疾病不得不住进医院。这次她住院治疗两个多月。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>17</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>11</span></span><span>日，四川犍为县双溪乡李兴文，在郫县犀浦打工工伤没得到赔偿，他到郫县劳动局申请工伤认定。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>18</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>12</span></span><span>日，成都市青羊区金沙街道强拆访民刘存钦，因房屋被拆近十年没解决，以及近十年维权被残酷打压，家庭成员承受不了这样的打压而出现矛盾，最后走上法庭。今天是她争养小孙女抚养权的诉讼案的开庭时间。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>19</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>13</span></span><span>日，成都市锦江区水井坊黄莉等五名群众代表，到草市街省市政务中心上访。今天是规划局局长进大厅接待群众。王松涛局长接待了她。起初局长忽悠她的问题，在黄莉反复解释、坚持下局长答应等调查后答复她。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>20</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>14</span></span><span>日，成都市锦江区访民郭玉彬、李发清、唐德英，到区信访办上访。接待人员推诿塘塞后，匆匆结束接待。无任何说法。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>21</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>14</span></span><span>日，金牛严塔凤、青羊帅正秀和叶俊华、新都叶尚洪四人进京上访，在美领事馆前被挡获行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>7</span></span><span>天。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>22</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>14</span></span><span>日，成都高新区学生＂右派＂罗开文，到省公安厅询问他今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>3</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>19</span></span><span>上交的复议材料的答复。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>07024</span></span><span>警员答复，叫他这段时间不要来公安厅了，本月底通知一块到公安厅复核处查询。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>049351</span></span><span>警察在场。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>23</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>15</span></span><span>日，成都高新区学生＂右派＂罗开文，收到青羊区法院他诉成都市公安局不作为的行政诉讼立案通知书。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>24 </span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>15</span></span><span>日，成都市锦江区访民郭玉彬、唐德英，到区人大上访。由仲主任接待。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>25</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>15</span></span><span>日，成都青羊区强拆访民董春模北京来电！今天晚上，她已经由市驻京办从马家楼接到托月宾馆。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>「上期遗漏补充」：</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>1</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>9</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>24</span></span><span>日，成都市锦江区访民李仁玉到省高院讯问她前夫被冤入狱申诉的立案情况。没任何说法。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>9</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>25</span></span><span>日，成都市青羊区人民北路街道办强拆访民陈茜丈夫林龙华，在家对冲进她家对他行凶的不明人员采取正当防卫而被行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>天。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>『四川省成都市外地区“简报”』</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>1</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>9</span></span><span>日，资阳乐自金顺镇水平石包村</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>组李孝文，到成都市人大上访，人大开了个让她到市政府上访的归口单。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span> </span></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2</span></span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>10</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>14</span></span><span>，资阳乐自高石镇</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>2</span></span><span>村</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>8</span></span><span>组龙生和，因他</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>40</span></span><span>多年前房屋被地方政府强占到省纪委上访。纪委推萎他到政府解决。到省政府后，政府接待人员说省委也可以管他的事，让他接着找政府。随后又到省纪委，纪委又推他到政府。</span></div>\n<p><span> </span></div>\n</div>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}